        public static SignalAspect mostRestrictive(SignalAspect first,
                           SignalAspect second)
        Tests two Aspects and determines which is more restrictive. The concept of "most restrictive" refers to which aspect enforces the most limitations of movement to a train. In Railcraft the primary use is in Signal Box logic.
